"Abstract The European Commission has made the next move towards the harmonization of liability legislation in Europe. After the enforcement of a directive regarding the liability for defective products in 1985 (further: the Directive), the Commission has published a proposal for a directive concerning the liability for services (further: the Proposal). In this article the outlines of the Proposal will be sketched. The Proposal will, furthermore, on some points be compared with the Directive."
